sql:
SELECT asn_id, COUNT(*) as prefix_count
FROM prefixes
GROUP BY asn_id;

external_knowledge:
Highest severity anomalies refer to anomalies with the most critical severity level (e.g., high); 
The ASN name refers to the name of the Autonomous System (ASN);
Total frequency represents the sum of frequencies of traffic events for each ASN on a specific date.

sql:
SELECT asn_number
FROM asns
WHERE country = 'United States';
